FBI UFO Archive KR — Public OCR + Translation Dataset
License: CC0 1.0 Universal (Public Domain Dedication) — PROPOSED, NOT YET FINAL

Source PDFs (`docs/ufo*.pdf`) are believed to be U.S. federal government works
in the public domain in the United States, distributed via the FBI Vault
(https://vault.fbi.gov/UFO). The OCR-derived English source layer is a
mechanical extraction and structural review layer.

Korean translation exports in this dataset are unofficial project-generated
translations. They are included under the same interim public dataset policy,
but final license selection is still pending.

The project owner intends to release this dataset under CC0 1.0
(https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/), but final license
selection is pending review of:
  1. U.S. federal government work copyright status outside the United States.
  2. Any third-party material attached to the source PDFs (newspaper clippings,
     letters from named individuals).
  3. Copyright and license treatment for project-generated Korean translations.

Until this LICENSE is replaced with a final license declaration, the dataset
should be treated as "for archival, research, and translation use, with
attribution requested." Redistribution under that interim policy is allowed
provided this notice is preserved.

NOT AFFILIATED WITH THE U.S. FBI OR THE U.S. GOVERNMENT.
